{"name":"Gria Trait Alt - Erdane Guardian","type":"feat","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/ffxiv_icons/FFXIVIcons-MainCommand%20-%20Others/03_MainCommands/07/character_configuration.png","system":{"description":{"value":"<h2>Alternate Racial Traits</h2><p>The following alternate racial traits may be selected in place of one or more of the standard racial traits above. Consult your GM before selecting any of these new options.</p><h2>Erdane Guardian:</h2><p>Bending the earth to their will was the calling of the ancient gria earth mages. A gria who follows the calling of her ancestors gains a +2 bonus to Knowledge (nature) and Knowledge (geography) checks. These are considered class skills for the gria with this racial trait.</p><h5>This racial trait replaces athleticism and survivalist.</h5>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":""},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[{"_id":"CGTec9to","formula":"2","operator":"add","subTarget":"skill.kna","modifier":"racial","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"3Dil2CgW","formula":"2","operator":"add","subTarget":"skill.kge","modifier":"racial","priority":0,"value":0}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"racial","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{"acr":false,"apr":false,"blf":false,"clm":false,"crf":false,"dip":false,"dev":false,"dis":false,"dri":false,"esc":false,"fly":false,"han":false,"hea":false,"int":false,"kar":false,"kdu":false,"ken":false,"kge":false,"khi":false,"klo":false,"kna":false,"kno":false,"kpl":false,"kre":false,"kte":false,"lin":false,"nav":false,"per":f