{"name":"Viera Trait Alt - Misty Mind","type":"feat","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/ffxiv_icons/FFXIVIcons-MainCommand%20-%20Others/03_MainCommands/07/character_configuration.png","system":{"description":{"value":"<h2>Alternate Racial Traits</h2><p>The following alternate racial traits may be selected in place of one or more of the standard racial traits above. Consult your GM before selecting any of these new options.</p><h2>Misty Mind:</h2><p>Some viera aren’t interested in channeling magic outward, and instead have learned to use their natural connection to the Mist as a kind of shield. These viera gain a +2 racial bonus on Will saving throws to resist spells and spell-like abilities of the enfeebling (charm) and enfeebling (compulsion) subschools. In addition, if a viera fails such a save, it receives another save 1 round later to prematurely end the effect (assuming the spell or spell-like ability has a duration greater than 1 round). This second save is made at the same DC as the first. If the viera has a similar ability from another source, it can only use one of these abilities per round, but can try the other on the second round if the first reroll ability fails.</p><h5>This racial trait replaces elemental summoner.</h5>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Viera Racial","Alt Trait"],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":""},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[{"text":"+[[2]] racial bonus on Will saving throws to resist spells and spell-like abilities of the enfeebling (charm) and enfeebling (compulsion) subschools","subTarget":"will"},{"text":"In addition, if a viera fails such a save, it receives another save 1 round later to prematurely end the effect (assuming the spell or spell-like ability has a duration greater than 1 round). This second save is made at the same DC as the first","subTarget":"will"}],"links":